title: How am I still honor level 2???
body: I literally play like every day since the honor leveling system came out, and I have not gotten punished since january 2015. I get honors frequently, and am still fucking honor level 2 after like 3 months. what is this??

replies.body: Everyone ranks up at a different pace due to simply playing a different amount of games and getting a different amount of honors than other people. I did check for you, and you're still gaining honor at the normal rate.
ok lmao another month goes by and no change?? is my account bugged?
